==English==
===Pronunciation===
* [[IPA]] /'kɒmjunɪzm/
===Etymology===
A translation of German [[Kommunismus]], from Marx and Engels's ''Manifesto of the German Communist Party'', from [[common]].
===Noun===
'''communism'''
#An economic philosophy supporting the common ownership of resources.

===Proper Noun===
'''Communism'''
#The system in which the government owns most property and runs the economy. The government is run by a single autocratic political party.

